by direct contact &amp; the cases of<lb/>
communication constitute the law<lb/>
of Temperature. -<lb/>
When the equal quantities of<lb/>
the same kind of matter of diff-<lb/>
erent temperatures are brought<lb/>
into contact till they acquire an<lb/>
equilibrium - the degree of Heat<lb/>
