18<lb/>
latent Heat or Caloric of combination -<lb/>
Water at all temperatures between<lb/>
212°and 32 seems to be possessed of<lb/>
the same capacity for heat and<lb/>
its powers of communicating Heat to<lb/>
bodies may under these circumst-<lb/>
